# iOS app background

The iOS app background is **only** these three elements, defined in `artifacts/vndrly-mobile/components/iosAppBackgroundSettings.tsx`:

1. Background color (`#2e3135`)
2. Header image (`ios-app-background-header.png`) fading into the color
3. Halftone pattern

Mount `IosAppBackgroundStack` **once** in `app/_layout.tsx` only.

**Forbidden:** `nav-pane-tokens`, `NavPaneChrome*`, `AppChromeShell`, `header-blur-asset`, logo PNGs in the background stack, extra background token files, changing `constants/colors.ts` for this purpose, or any fourth background layer/setting.

Screen roots must not paint an opaque color over the stack (use transparent). Do not add background policy elsewhere.
